News Reporter Ghost: It's a terrible thing I've done, but... if I'm willing to change, that's what matters.
News Reporter Ghost: I recognize my errors, and... I need to go find Lawyer Ghost and talk to him.
News Reporter Ghost: I need to go find that person in the afterlife and apologize.
News Reporter Ghost: I can't fix everything, but I can at least make amends and give them and myself... peace.
